EmailTemplate.name: SunPower Residential Lease Dealer Participation Agreement
EmailTemplate.subject: SunPower Residential Lease Dealer Participation Agreement (DPA)
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear SunPower Partner,
Thank you for your interest in the SunPower Lease Program. Your SunPower Sales Manager has requested we forward the SunPower Residential Lease Dealer Participation Agreement (DPA) for your review and signature.
We use an online signature technology - EchoSign - that complies with all legal standards and attaches a digital signature to secure electronic documents. Please look for an email from EchoSign in the next few minutes. You will need to electronically sign the DPA document, as well as complete a few fields. Once signed, a fully executed copy will be returned to you within one week for good standing order of your files.
We recognize that this is a long legal document. It is important that you review and understand the requirements of the program prior to signing the agreement. We would like to call out a few features from the agreement and encourage you to discuss this with your SunPower Sales Manager.
Partners must enroll as a SunPower supplier to be able to participate (see Exhibit G of the DPA for requirements). Please send your updated licenses and insurance to residentialamericascompliance@sunpower.com. Attached in this email is a zip file that contains examples of some of the documents that are required to enroll.
Partners and their participating sales representatives must complete and pass the Lease Program Certification exams prior to quoting or selling the SunPower Lease.
If you need to update your employee contact records in the Partner Portal, please send an email to partnerportal@sunpower.com requesting for portal access for employees who will be creating quotes or lease documents.
After the agreement is executed, you will receive access to our lease training and information modules through the Partner Portal. You will not be able to transact a lease until you are set up as a SunPower supplier and have passed the required certification exams.
The table below shows the required certifications.
Certification Title
Minimum Requirements
Lease Dealer Participation Agreement (DPA) Exam
1 Dealer Principal and 1 lease administrator
Lease Energy Estimation Course and Exam
Patner Salesperson must pass this course
Lease Terms & Conditions Course and Exam
Partner Salesperson must pass this course
Associate Residential Design
1 person per dealer
Associate Residential Installation
1 person per dealer
For your questions regarding access to the Partner Portal, please send an email to partnerportal@sunpower.com.
For questions on the documents that you need to submit, please send an email to residentialamericascompliance@sunpower.com.
For questions or concerns regarding the online lessons at the SunPower University, please send an email to trainingsupport@sunpower.com.
Thank you for your partnership. We look forward to working with you for years to come.
Regards,
SunPower Lease Program
